{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781716692836,"sessionID":"ses_12969ccceffeNZhLAWy8uWT1Wq","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_02_oeaOLGgdtbdFSpQ6HBN72323","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p021-deepseek-1/deep-review-findings-registry.json","content":"{\n  \"sessionId\": \"fanout-p021-deepseek-1-1781716627766-f4z8n0\",\n  \"generation\": 1,\n  \"lineageMode\": \"new\",\n  \"openFindings\": [],\n  \"resolvedFindings\": [],\n  \"blockedStopHistory\": [],\n  \"persistentSameSeverity\": [],\n  \"severityChanged\": [],\n  \"repeatedFindings\": [],\n  \"dimensionCoverage\": {\n    \"correctness\": false,\n    \"security\": false,\n    \"traceability\": false,\n    \"maintainability\": false\n  },\n  \"findingsBySeverity\": {\n    \"P0\": 0,\n    \"P1\": 0,\n    \"P2\": 0\n  },\n  \"openFindingsCount\": 0,\n  \"resolvedFindingsCount\": 0,\n  \"convergenceScore\": 0,\n  \"graphConvergenceScore\": 0,\n  \"graphDecision\": null,\n  \"graphBlockers\": [],\n  \"corruptionWarnings\": []\n}\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p021-deepseek-1/deep-review-findings-registry.json","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p021-deepseek-1/deep-review-findings-registry.json","time":{"start":1781716692833,"end":1781716692835}},"id":"prt_ed6972767001hp1S0LZBT6qvLe","sessionID":"ses_12969ccceffeNZhLAWy8uWT1Wq","messageID":"msg_ed696f03f001unmNQmcd5bDcsF"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781716700465,"sessionID":"ses_12969ccceffeNZhLAWy8uWT1Wq","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_03_3SRvI465MNrHhqxIxoon4076","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p021-deepseek-1/deep-review-strategy.md","content":"# Deep Review Strategy\n\n## topic\nReview of 021-cooperative-heavy-phases: daemon responsiveness instrumentation, trigger-embedding-backfill chunking, and per-tail-phase marker refresh.\n\n## review-dimensions\n- [ ] Correctness\n- [ ] Security\n- [ ] Traceability\n- [ ] Maintainability\n\n## completed-dimensions\n(None yet)\n\n## running-findings\n- P0: 0 | P1: 0 | P2: 0 active\n\n## what-worked\n(None yet)\n\n## what-failed\n(None yet)\n\n## exhausted-approaches\n(None yet)\n\n## ruled-out-directions\n(None yet)\n\n## next-focus\n**Correctness** (Priority 1): Verify the event-loop lag sampler and `timedPhase` wrapper behave correctly (no yield inside transactions, gate on `ctx.onPhase` preserves synchronous path, `loopLagTimer` cleanup in `finally` block, `maxLoopLagMs` logging).\n\n## known-context\n- Spec status: Complete (code); deploy-time lag read pending\n- Completion: 100%\n- The spec adds instrumentation (event-loop lag sampler + `timedPhase`) in `memory-index.ts`, chunks `trigger-embedding-backfill.ts` into per-chunk transactions with between-chunk yields, and wraps tail phases with marker refresh on entry.\n- No `checklist.md` exists (Level 1 spec folder).\n- No `resource-map.md` for this spec folder. Skipping coverage gate.\n- Verification: typecheck, trigger-backfill unit tests (6/6 including 3 new cancel/yield cases), scan-job suite, daemon-reelection adoption harness all pass.\n- Pre-existing failures noted, not introduced: `retry-manager.vitest.ts` T49, `handler-memory-index-cooldown`, `handler-memory-index-needs-rebuild`, `trigger-threshold-tuning`.\n\n## cross-reference-status\n| Protocol | Level | Status | Gate | Notes |\n|----------|-------|--------|------|-------|\n| spec_code | core | pending | hard | Spec claims must resolve to shipped behavior |\n| checklist_evidence | core | n/a | hard | No checklist.md (Level 1) |\n| feature_catalog_code | overlay | pending | advisory | Cross-check spec-scoped features against implementation |\n| playbook_capability | overlay | pending | advisory | Validate operational playbook scenarios |\n\n## files-under-review\n| File | Dimension(s) | Status |\n|------|-------------|--------|\n| `mcp_server/handlers/memory-index.ts` (1587 lines) | Correctness, Security, Traceability, Maintainability | pending |\n| `mcp_server/lib/search/trigger-embedding-backfill.ts` (344 lines) | Correctness, Security, Traceability, Maintainability | pending |\n| `mcp_server/tests/trigger-embedding-backfill.vitest.ts` (216 lines) | Correctness, Traceability | pending |\n\n## review-boundaries\n- Max iterations: 1\n- Convergence threshold: 0.10\n- Stuck threshold: 2\n- Severity threshold: P2\n- Execution mode: auto\n- resource-map.md not present. Skipping coverage gate.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p021-deepseek-1/deep-review-strategy.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p021-deepseek-1/deep-review-strategy.md","time":{"start":1781716700460,"end":1781716700465}},"id":"prt_ed6972fa8001eB51nYBosU9PKF","sessionID":"ses_12969ccceffeNZhLAWy8uWT1Wq","messageID":"msg_ed696f03f001unmNQmcd5bDcsF"}}
